Brief installation instructions 
BATH (Oct 2022)

Install source code from GitHub:
   git clone https://github.com/TravisWheelerLab/BATH.git
   cd BATH
   git clone https://github.com/TravisWheelerLab/easel
   (cd easel; git checkout BATH)
   autoconf
   ./configure
   make
   make check                        # optional: automated tests
   make install                      # optional: install BATH programs and man pages





